LIFE LEECH

Usage       : cast 'life leech'
Accumulative: -
Duration    : instantaneous
Save        : Versus spell

   This area affect spell sucks a moderate amount of energy from everyone in
the room.  The energy drained is then added to the anti-paladins hit points.
It is a more powerful version of vampiric touch.  The amount of damage is
dependant on level.  This is an antipaladins most powerful spell. 

See also: VAMPIRIC TOUCH
Related Topics: SPELL INFO, ANTIPALADINS
